Anyway, Bip's right, you deal more damage with a better ratio weapon offhand, no iffs ands or butts, excepting ultra high mitigation baddies, when you don't have enough attack rating (PS you need 1500+ attack rating to hit well against those buggers).  Centi LS will ALWAYS outdamage Lammy offhand, except in that rare case stated above.  <br>
